      <h1 class='title'>Oil and Gas Production</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 15 January 2004 vol 416 c48WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_48ws' title='Col. 48WS &mdash; HC Deb 15 January 2004 vol 416 c48WS' name='column_48ws' href='#column_48ws' rel='bookmark'>48WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0416P2_20040115_CWS_13'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-stephen-timms' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0416P2_20040115_CWS_13' title='Link to this speech by Mr Stephen Timms' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-stephen-timms" title="Mr Stephen Timms">The Minister for Energy, E-Commerce and Postal Services (Mr. Stephen Timms)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I am pleased to inform the House that I am today offering ATP Oil and Gas (UK) Ltd. an oil and gas production licence on seaward block 2/15 in the northern North Sea.</p><p>The successful applicant will have a fixed period in which to decide whether or not to accept the offers.</p><p>The DTI undertook an environmental screening assessment to ensure compliance with environmental legislation, and concluded that
          <q>the screening had not identified any environmental concern that would prejudice the offering of block 2/15 for licence".</q></p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
